data.description: This lovey 4-bedroom 2.5 bath sits on a double corner lot in the heart of Alice, Texas. Has a nice size living room with an additional room adjacent to living area. There is also a separate dining room next to the kitchen. Spacious 2-car garage with tons of storage space. Brand NEW roof with a huge backyard. Call your favorite realtor to schedule a showing. Seller will install BRAND NEW kitchen appliances! ( stove, oven range, dishwasher) Also, will give a $5000 buyer credit towards closing costs.
